ています。\n\n更新処理では、これらのカラムに加えて更新者IDと更新日時も記録する必要があります。画面仕様として、ユーザ情報更新画面と確認画面のイメージが含まれています。 今、ユーザ情報更新機能の画面遷移と処理フローをまとめている。各画面IDとリクエストIDの対応関係を整理して、更新画面の初期表示から戻る処理まで、システムの動作パターンを定義している。 Now I'm looking at the USERS table structure, mapping out all the columns I need to handle in the update process—user ID, names in both kanji and kana, email, extension numbers for the building and personal lines, and mobile phone numbers broken down by area code and local number. Now I'm looking at the validation rules for the name fields—both the kanji and kana versions need to be required, use the correct character types, and stay within the 50-character limit. Then I'm mapping out which columns get updated during the process, focusing on the name fields and the audit timestamps.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":22797,"cache_read_input_tokens":29889,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":22797,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"12de1b25-7f3f-45ff-a3d9-ecc430ea4111","uuid":"7305b16b-ac73-499b-a030-501f32cff1f3"}
